parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description:
The end of the time range to create the diagnostic report. This value is a UNIX timestamp representing the number of milliseconds that have elapsed since January 1, 1970, 00:00:00 UTC.

>  The start time must be later than the end time.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to create the diagnostic report. This value is a UNIX timestamp representing the number of milliseconds that have elapsed since January 1, 1970, 00:00:00 UTC.
